Package com.example.freeturilo.core

Class RouteParameters

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.example.freeturilo.core.RouteParameters
  • public class RouteParameters
extends java.lang.Object
    A bundle of route calculation parameters.

    Object of this class represents a bundle of parameters used in calculation of a NextBike bicycle route. It encapsulates the start, end and stops of the route and the criterion of the route's calculation.
